               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1813" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1813" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1813" type="surname" value="WATSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1813" type="given" value="ELIZABETH CATHERINE"></interp>ELIZABETH CATHERINE WATSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at the White Horse public-house at Charlton, near Woolwich. On the 12th of June I was at Deptford fair—the prisoner pressed by my left side, put his hand over my right shoulder, and took the pin out of my breast—I caught hold of his arm before he got his hand off my shoulder—the pin was in his hand—I am sure it was quite out of my clothes—he got his hand from me, and I caught hold of the skirt of his coat—my brother called a policeman—I saw the prisoner drop the pin—a little boy picked it up, and gave it to me—I gave it to the officer.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1814" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1814" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
