                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1814" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WATSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was with my sister—the prisoner pressed against her, and she said, "George, this man has got my pin"—I laid hold of his collar directly, and the policeman being close at hand came up directly—the prisoner dropped the pin by his leg, and a boy picked it up.</p>
               <p>
